This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques for clinical named entity recognition (NER). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also uses recurrent neural network (RNN) models, which are a popular machine learning technique, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. The paper also deals with information retrieval (IR) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, so cs.IR and cs.AI are also possible categories. Finally, the paper deals with clinical NER, which is a specific application area, so cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category.
